<Defs>
  <VEF.Abilities.AbilityDef ParentName="VPE_PsycastBase">
    <defName>VPEMYX_FleshHealing</defName>
    <label>畸体补全</label>
    <description>虚空从不吝啬它的“仁慈”，但这种仁慈往往令人毛骨悚然。引导深渊能量，瞬间治愈目标身上的常规伤势；若目标存在器官或肢体缺失，缺失部位将被强制生长出对应的黑暗超凡器官/肢体进行替代。</description>
    <iconPath>UI/Abilities/VPEMYX/VPEMYX_FleshHealing</iconPath>
    <abilityClass>VPE_MyExtension.Ability_FleshHealing</abilityClass>
    <castTime>120</castTime>
    <range>12.9</range>
    <targetMode>Pawn</targetMode>
    <showUndrafted>true</showUndrafted>
