  <VEF.Abilities.AbilityDef ParentName="VPE_PsycastBase">
    <defName>VPEMYX_DelusionBackflow</defName>
    <label>妄念倒灌</label>
    <description>向目标脑海灌入虚空呓语。敌人会陷入重度精神崩溃；友军会获得短时无痛与高机动，但心情大幅下降。</description>
